TITLE: Defining Converter Type Structure for Open Next.js Backends
DESCRIPTION: Defines the type structure for converters, which are used to convert events and results between different formats. Includes the Converter type that extends BaseOverride.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opennextjs/docs/blob/main/pages/aws/inner_workings/components/overview.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
export type Converter<
  E extends BaseEventOrResult = InternalEvent,
  R extends BaseEventOrResult = InternalResult,
> = BaseOverride & {
  convertFrom: (event: any) => Promise<E>;
  convertTo: (result: R, originalRequest?: any) => any;
};
```

